{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MS12_090.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x10,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "...And that's why I'm thinking about making a tent."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, a tent, you say... That's rather general, there are many types of tents..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. Since I'm going through the trouble, I want to make an amazing one. One that can fit lots of people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Since I'm going to take an exam for alchemists, it would be a problem if I couldn't do Synthesis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "In that case... The tent would need to be big enough for a cauldron..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, also, while I'm at it, I'd like to put a bed, and a study desk inside..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "S-Sophie? I think what you're describing is drifting further and further away from a \"tent\"..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "It's done! This is the recipe for my tent!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x47,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "The outside looks like a normal tent. And if I fold it up, it fits inside my bag!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "But the inside is really amazing. It's like a regular room in a house!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "There's a cauldron, and a bed, and a desk... And even bookshelves. Hehehe... I've come up with something great..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You've come up with a recipe that defies the laws of physics, on a whim... You really have grown..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Really? Isn't this normal?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "...Uu. It seems as compensation for your growth, you've lost common sense..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat, that's not true. Don't be rude."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Oh well, whatever. Now that the recipe is done... All I need to do is Synthesize the tent real quick!"
        }
    ]
}